Package: NetHypGeom
Type: Package
Title: Hyperbolic geometry of complex networks
Version: 0.9
Date: 2017-03-03
Author: Gregorio Alanis-Lobato, Pablo Mier, Miguel A. Andrade-Navarro
Maintainer: Gregorio Alanis-Lobato <galanisl@uni-mainz.de>
Description: Tools for the generation, analysis and visualisation of complex networks in hyperbolic space. 
	It includes the Popularity-Similarity model, a method to grow artifical networks inside a hyperbolic circle,
	and LaBNE+HM, a method for the fast yet accurate embedding of complex networks into the native representation 
	of the two-dimensional hyperbolic plane.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.1), igraph (>= 1.0), ggplot2 (>= 2.2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.3), RSpectra (>= 0.12.0), scales (>= 0.4.1)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
LinkingTo: Rcpp
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
BugReports: https://github.com/galanisl/NetHypGeom/issues
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
